cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with the problem of texture classification using soft computing techniques such as neural networks and fuzzy logic. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves training and optimization of the soft computing models, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of DCT coefficients for texture classification also involves signal processing, which is covered under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves the comparison of different soft computing models, which falls under the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
